      "text": "It is because of refraction of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 68320.0,
      "end_time": 73620.0,
      "text": "Refraction of light is the change in direction of light when it passes from one medium to another obliquely."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 75580.0,
      "end_time": 77940.0,
