      "text": "They are air and water."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 94840.0,
      "end_time": 98860.0,
      "text": "When the light rays coming from the tip of the magic wand pass from water to air."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 98860.0,
      "end_time": 102540.0,
      "text": "They change their direction, that is, they get refracted."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 103980.0,
      "end_time": 109160.0,
      "text": "When these refracted rays reach our eyes, our eyes trace them backward as straight lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 110840.0,
      "end_time": 115840.0,
      "text": "Due to this, the rays appear to come from a point slightly above the original position."
    },
    {
